  "title": "Staff Nurse (GERIATRIC/GOVT) - East/up to $4500 #HAO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $4500</p><p>Working Days & Hours: any 5 days, 3 shifts</p><p>Location: Bedok/Pasir Ris</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>Utilize clinical judgement, critical thinking and evidence based care (research based) in the delivery of resident care</p><p>Work collaboratively with other healthcare professionals to deliver coordinated and holistic care</p><p>Coordinate continuity of care throughout hospitalization and transition to home/community</p><p>Act as a liaison between residents, care givers and multi-discipline healthcare professionals and communicate effectively on the care plan and discharge planning</p><p>Provide clinical guidance and direction to junior nurses (EN, HCA, CA & Therapy Assistant)</p><p>Contribute In-service Education program</p><p>Job Requirements: Min VALID SNB & BCLS w min 2 yrs of relevant perm inpatient ward experience</p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</a><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
